Package com.atakmap.android.util

Class ReservationService<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.util.ReservationService<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of object being reserved. Compared using equals.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileCache
    public class ReservationService<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides simple thread-safe reservation of objects. Reservation requests are blocked until the requested object is available for reservation.

      • reserve

        public ReservationService.Reservation<T> reserve​(T item)
        Attempts to reserve the supplied item. Blocks the calling thread until the item is reserved.
        Parameters:
        item - The item to be reserved.
        Returns:
        A Reservation if the reservation was completed; null if the thread was interrupted.

      • tryReserve

        public ReservationService.Reservation<T> tryReserve​(T item)
        Attempts to reserve the supplied item. Balks if the item is already reserved.
        Parameters:
        item - The item to be reserved.
        Returns:
        A Reservation if the reservation was completed; null if the thread was interrupted.

      • tryWithReservation

        public boolean tryWithReservation​(T item,
                                  java.lang.Runnable r)
        Runs the supplied Runnable after trying to establishing a reservation for the supplied item. Balks if the item is already reserved. Releases the reservation after the Runnable has executed.
        Parameters:
        item - The item to be reserved while the Runnable executes.
        r - The Runnable to be executed while the item is reserved.
        Returns:
        True if the reservation was completed; false if the item was already reserved.

      • unreserve
